summary: This mod adds Solar Elves, which regenerate Magicka, Stamina, and Health very quickly in the sunlight, half as fast at night, are immune to all diseases, and can naturally use a powerful form of sun magic.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds Solar Elves, which regenerate Magicka, Stamina, and Health very quickly in the sunlight, half as fast at night, are immune to all diseases, and can naturally use a powerful form of sun magic.

This mod requires Dawnguard.

If anyone has a suggestion, don't hesitate to leave it in the comments!!!
author: Bable631
